Description: OMARCHY-inspired workflow and aesthetics for COSMIC Desktop
 COSMIC ORDER brings OMARCHY-style workflow to COSMIC Desktop with theme
 management, tool theme sync (Ghostty, btop, Neovim, Zellij, fzf, lazygit),
 terminal screensaver with session lock, power-aware profiles, and a
 scriptable CLI interface.
 .
 The terminal screensaver renders with TerminalTextEffects, which is not in the
 Debian/Ubuntu archive; install it with: pipx install terminaltexteffects
